  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape Together is a VR Escape Room game, that features both singleplayer and multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/3b43f5c8d89c3087ba227d93fa394248.poster.avif?t=1748462173\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/3b43f5c8d89c3087ba227d93fa394248.webm?t=1748462173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/3b43f5c8d89c3087ba227d93fa394248.mp4?t=1748462173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather your best mystery solving team or go in alone, it's time to take on The Secrets Of The Professor...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/21e88809d45a7496cb96611d4ac079be.poster.avif?t=1748462173\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/21e88809d45a7496cb96611d4ac079be.webm?t=1748462173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/21e88809d45a7496cb96611d4ac079be.mp4?t=1748462173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The professor has invited you, his best students, to his house, but do you know what you are getting yourself into? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help the professor, and uncover his secrets as you explore his house. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BUT, be quick - the timer is ticking! It looks like some agents followed you on your way to the house, and they don't seem friendly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck students, your professor is counting on you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VR Crossplatform support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play with all your friends no matter what VR headset they have!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Proximity chat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In-game proximity chat for increased immersion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements and items</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For most achievement you unlock, you also unlock an item in the game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A lot of puzzles in Escape Together: Secrets of the Professor are color based, which makes the game unsuitable for colorblind players</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape Together is a VR Escape Room game, that features both singleplayer and multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/3b43f5c8d89c3087ba227d93fa394248.poster.avif?t=1748462173\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/3b43f5c8d89c3087ba227d93fa394248.webm?t=1748462173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/3b43f5c8d89c3087ba227d93fa394248.mp4?t=1748462173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather your best mystery solving team or go in alone, it's time to take on The Secrets Of The Professor...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/21e88809d45a7496cb96611d4ac079be.poster.avif?t=1748462173\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/21e88809d45a7496cb96611d4ac079be.webm?t=1748462173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393820/extras/21e88809d45a7496cb96611d4ac079be.mp4?t=1748462173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The professor has invited you, his best students, to his house, but do you know what you are getting yourself into? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help the professor, and uncover his secrets as you explore his house. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BUT, be quick - the timer is ticking! It looks like some agents followed you on your way to the house, and they don't seem friendly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck students, your professor is counting on you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VR Crossplatform support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play with all your friends no matter what VR headset they have!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Proximity chat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In-game proximity chat for increased immersion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements and items</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For most achievement you unlock, you also unlock an item in the game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A lot of puzzles in Escape Together: Secrets of the Professor are color based, which makes the game unsuitable for colorblind players</i></p>",
